description:
Clear out hidden items and trinkets in a new set of beautifully arranged in themes such as 50s Diners, Groceries, Fancy Jewelry, Science Laboratory, and many more! 
Enjoy playing a variety of mini-games and collect little trinkets as you go along!

Collector's Edition includes:
- Play over 100 games!
- Make gameplay simpler with Help and Hint functions!
- Includes 8 extra themes
- 1 more collection room
name: So Much Stuff 2 Collector's Edition
